, the enhanced rate shall be $1.77 per hour and shall be adjusted using actuarial analysis based on the cost of care. Effective July 1, 2016.", "pending_committee_id": 254, "committee": {"committee_id": 254, "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 36, "name": "Assignments"}, "referrals": [{"date": "2016-02-17", "committee_id": 254, "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 36, "name": "Assignments"}, {"date": "2016-03-01", "committee_id": 274, "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 36, "name": "Human Services"}, {"date": "2016-07-31", "committee_id": 254, "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 36, "name": "Assignments"}], "history": [{"date": "2016-02-17", "action": "Filed with Secretary by Sen. Kwame Raoul", "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 36, "importance": 1}, {"date": "2016-02-17", "action": "First Reading", "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 36, "importance": 0}, {"date": "2016-02-17", "action": "Referred to Assignments", "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 36, "importance": 1}, {"date": "2016-02-18", "action": "Added as Chief Co-Sponsor Sen. Jacqueline Y. Collins", "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 36, "importance": 0}, {"date": "2016-02-29", "action": "Added as Chief Co-Sponsor Sen. Patricia Van Pelt", "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 36, "importance": 0}, {"date": "2016-02-29", "action": "Added as Co-Sponsor Sen. Daniel Biss", "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 36, "importance": 0}, {"date": "2016-03-01", "action": "Added as Co-Sponsor Sen. Heather A. Steans", "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 36, "importance": 0}, {"date": "2016-03-01", "action": "Assigned to Human Services", "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 36, "importance": 1}, {"date": "2016-03-01", "action": "Added as Chief Co-Sponsor Sen. Toi W. Hutchinson", "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 36, "importance": 0}, {"date": "2016-03-01", "action": "Added as Chief Co-Sponsor Sen. Kimberly A. Lightford", "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 36, "importance": 0}, {"date": "2016-03-02", "action": "Added as Co-Sponsor Sen. John G. Mulroe", "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 36, "importance": 0}, 